author: Msnbc
title: Georgia's Kemp just learned what most already knew about virus
description: The chief executive of a large state didn't know until a couple of days ago that asymptomatic people can transmit the virus?
content: Georgia has been slower than most states to impose restrictions intended to slow the spread of the coronavirus, and those delays have resulted in awful consequences throughout the state. Yesterday, finally, Gov. Brian Kemp (R) announced a stay-at-home order, … [+1664 chars]
